br.com.caelum.vraptor.util.test

Class MockResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.com.caelum.vraptor.core.AbstractResult
      • br.com.caelum.vraptor.util.test.MockResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Result
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MockHttpResult, MockSerializationResult

    @Component
public class MockResult
extends AbstractResult
    A mocked Result for testing your controllers. It will ignore redirections and accumulates included objects, so you can use result.included() for inspect included objects.
    Author:
    Lucas Cavalcanti, Guilherme Silveira
